OL,3,CPolice appeal after woman raped by
OL,4,C'several men' outside church in Surrey
OL,6,FPolice are investigating a rape,
OL,7,Fbelieved to have taken place outside
OL,8,Fof a Church, in the early hours of
OL,9,FSaturday morning.
OL,11,FIn a social media post, Surrey Police
OL,12,Fsaid a woman in her 20s, reported that
OL,13,Fshe was attacked by several men after
OL,14,Fshe was followed leaving a nightclub.
OL,16,FThe incident is believed to have taken
OL,17,Fplace outside Epsom Methodist Church
OL,18,Fon Ashley Road, between 2am and 4am.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
