OL,3,CPolice appeal after woman raped by
OL,4,C'several men' outside church in Surrey
OL,6,FThe force added that it currently did
OL,7,Fnot have "full descriptions of the
OL,8,Fsuspects" and are "working hard" on
OL,9,Fthis.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Aine Matthews said:
OL,13,F"We understand this is an extremely
OL,14,Fdistressing incident and the victim is
OL,15,Fbeing supported by specialist officers.
OL,17,F"Our investigation is in its early
OL,18,Fstages and a team of officers have
OL,19,Fbeen conducting extensive enquiries
OL,20,Ftoday to identify and locate the
OL,21,Fsuspects.
OL,26,@oD@JOUpD@IO]pD@SOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
