OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776164568
OL,3,CPolice appeal after woman raped by
OL,4,C'several men' outside church in Surrey
OL,6,F"We are working at pace to develop our
OL,7,Fpicture of the suspects and we will
OL,8,Fshare details as soon we are able to.
OL,10,F"Officers remain in the area and I
OL,11,Fencourage you to speak with them if
OL,12,Fyou have any concerns.
OL,14,F"As part of our investigation, we
OL,15,Fwould like to speak to anyone who was
OL,16,Fin the area between 2am and 4am and
OL,17,Fmay have been seen or spoken to a
OL,18,Fwoman in her 20s in distress."
